articles.author: TOI Sports Desk
articles.title: 'It's good learning for us': Suryakumar Yadav lauds South Africa's batting after defeat in 2nd T20I - IndiaTimes
articles.description: Cricket News: South Africa registered a crucial victory against India in a rain-curtailed match at St George's Park, taking 1-0 lead in the three-game T20I series.
